channel.description: Extremum Spiritum is Latin for "Dying Breath" or "Last Breath". We at Extremum Spiritum Paranormal are based out of South Central, Illinois. All of our videos and photos are 100% authentic filmed at location. Do you own a house or business in Southern Illinois that you believe is haunted? Contact us at extremumspiritumnews@gmail.com to arrange an investigation of your property or home. If we find that you do indeed have some type of entity haunting your place we will give you guidance on how to rid yourself of this problem. There is no charge.
